object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Ahead is a snail. Snails block exits and hidden areas. To kill snails push crates on top of them. Careful... pushing crates the wrong way might mean you need to reset the level.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: This is a switch. Press 'e' when near it to activate it and turn off the blocks in your way.
